  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 9th level, you gain a breath weapon. This breath weapon deals 1d6 points of damage of your energy type per sorcerer level. Those caught in the area of the breath receive a Reflex save for half damage. The DC of this save is equal to 10 + 1/2 your sorcerer level + your Charisma modifier. The shape of the breath weapon depends on your dragon type (as indicated on the above chart).</p><p>At 9th level, you can use this ability once per day. At 17th level, you can use this ability twice per day. At 20th level, you can use this ability three times per day.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Dragon Type</th><th>Energy Type</th><th>Breath Shape</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><span>Black</span></td><td><span>Acid</span></td><td><span>60-foot line</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Blue</span></td><td><span>Electricity</span></td><td><span>60-foot line</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Green</span></td><td><span>Acid</span></td><td><span>30-foot cone</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Red</span></td><td><span>Fire</span></td><td><span>30-foot cone</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>White</span></td><td><span>Cold</span></td><td><span>30-foot cone</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Brass</span></td><td><span>Fire</span></td><td><span>60-foot line</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Bronze</span></td><td><span>Electricity</span></td><td><span>60-foot line</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Copper</span></td><td><span>Acid</span></td><td><span>60-foot line</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Gold</span></td><td><span>Fire</span></td><td><span>30-foot cone</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Silver</span></td><td><span>Cold</span></td><td><span>30-foot cone</span></td></tr></tbody></table>"
